<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 20:08:13 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>加沙战争让以色列陷入困境，内塔尼亚胡的疯狂和狂妄自大得到充分展现</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/as-gaza-war-bogs-israel-down-netanyahus-madness-and-megalomania-are-on-full-display/00000190-2f9c-d700-a7f0-affe48be0000</link><description>甘茨离开后，战时内阁可能已经解散，但内塔尼亚胡领导的掠夺者内阁并没有浪费时间</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 19:48:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/as-gaza-war-bogs-israel-down-netanyahus-madness-and-megalomania-are-on-full-display/00000190-2f9c-d700-a7f0-affe48be0000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔说，他的以色列警察局长候选人毕业于弗吉尼亚大学。他没有</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-says-his-candidate-for-israel-police-chief-graduated-from-uva-he-didnt/00000190-31cd-d5f5-a5d6-f9ef1a2f0000</link><description>国家安全部长写道，Avshalom Peled 是“弗吉尼亚大学犯罪学项目的毕业生”，但《国土报》发现他在该机构的学习包括 1987 年为期六周、15 小时的 FBI 课程</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 19:42:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-says-his-candidate-for-israel-police-chief-graduated-from-uva-he-didnt/00000190-31cd-d5f5-a5d6-f9ef1a2f0000</guid></item><item><title>医院和大学工作人员在以色列警察袭击后抗议，并在反政府集会上逮捕医生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/hospital-workers-protest-after-israel-police-assault-arrest-doctors-at-anti-govt-rally/00000190-312a-d340-a1f8-392ec0970000</link><description>警察在治疗受伤的抗议者时袭击了一名医生并逮捕了另一名医生。医生们称这些事件“跨越了双方商定的界限”，这可能导致工作人员“出于对自身安全的恐惧”而拒绝在现场提供医疗服务</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 19:03:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/hospital-workers-protest-after-israel-police-assault-arrest-doctors-at-anti-govt-rally/00000190-312a-d340-a1f8-392ec0970000</guid></item><item><title>“不受欢迎”：以色列侨民团体发起运动，要求撤销内塔尼亚胡国会邀请</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/non-grata-israeli-expats-launch-campaign-to-get-netanyahu-congress-invite-rescinded/00000190-31a2-d4fa-ad9d-ffab47550000</link><description>UnXeptable 是一个领导了以色列侨民在全球举行的许多反内塔尼亚胡抗议活动的组织，如果内塔尼亚胡向国会发表讲话的邀请不被撤回，该组织打算在内塔尼亚胡讲话期间将一车的以色列裔美国人带到国会外抗议</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 18:12:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/non-grata-israeli-expats-launch-campaign-to-get-netanyahu-congress-invite-rescinded/00000190-31a2-d4fa-ad9d-ffab47550000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡表示，以色列国防军对摧毁哈马斯表示怀疑，以色列军队“有义务”实现政府设定的目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/netanyahu-says-army-obligated-to-goals-set-by-govt-after-idf-doubts-hamas-destruction/00000190-316e-d340-a1f8-396e91ac0000</link><description>以色列军方发言人丹尼尔·哈加里 (Daniel Hagari) 表示，“任何认为我们能够消灭哈马斯的人都是错误的”，因为政治领导人和以色列国防军领导人之间的紧张局势因加沙战斗的延长而持续加剧</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 17:47:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/netanyahu-says-army-obligated-to-goals-set-by-govt-after-idf-doubts-hamas-destruction/00000190-316e-d340-a1f8-396e91ac0000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔和内塔尼亚胡互相嘲笑，总理恳求联盟伙伴“控制住”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-netanyahu-trade-jeers-as-pm-implores-coalition-partners-to-get-a-grip/00000190-3075-d39e-a999-76ff6afd0000</link><description>本-格维尔、内塔尼亚胡和德里周二因试图确保政府对市政拉比任命拥有控制权的法案获得多数席位而产生分歧，随后发生冲突。该法案于周三被废除</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 17:32:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-netanyahu-trade-jeers-as-pm-implores-coalition-partners-to-get-a-grip/00000190-3075-d39e-a999-76ff6afd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 257 天：发言人称那些认为以色列国防军可以摧毁哈马斯的人是错误的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-257-those-who-think-idf-can-destroy-hamas-are-mistaken-spokesman-says/00000190-316e-dc02-a7d8-f17e7ec40000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡指责拜登推迟运送武器后，白宫取消了与以色列就伊朗问题举行的重要战略会议 ■ 以色列国家审计长表示，总理办公室要求他推迟对其 10 月 7 日前后行为的调查 ■ 约 25 枚火箭从黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射 ■ 联合国：无法由于加沙人的无法无天和恐慌，从加沙边境口岸分发援助物资 ■ 这是战争进入 257 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 17:04:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-257-those-who-think-idf-can-destroy-hamas-are-mistaken-spokesman-says/00000190-316e-dc02-a7d8-f17e7ec40000</guid></item><item><title>两名以色列定居者因用斧头袭击西岸巴勒斯坦家庭而被判入狱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/two-israeli-settlers-sentenced-to-prison-for-axe-attack-on-palestinian-family-in-west-bank/00000190-30ed-d39e-a999-76ef1a470000</link><description>这两名定居者因在 2023 年胡瓦拉骚乱期间出于种族动机袭击五名家庭成员并破坏汽车而被判处三年监禁。两人承认了对他们提出的指控</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 17:01:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/two-israeli-settlers-sentenced-to-prison-for-axe-attack-on-palestinian-family-in-west-bank/00000190-30ed-d39e-a999-76ef1a470000</guid></item><item><title>拜登还需要多少证据来证明内塔尼亚胡不是美国盟友？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.highlight/how-much-more-proof-does-biden-need-that-netanyahu-is-not-a-u-s-ally/00000190-30e8-d4fa-ad9d-ffe94ffa0000</link><description>本杰明·内塔尼亚胡在这段令人翻白眼的视频中指责美国人扣押了一批军火，并再次让人想起了温斯顿·丘吉尔，这是他在玩弄政治——这是他唯一知道该怎么做的事情。他七月份在国会发表讲话的邀请应该推迟到美国大选之后</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 15:45:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.highlight/how-much-more-proof-does-biden-need-that-netanyahu-is-not-a-u-s-ally/00000190-30e8-d4fa-ad9d-ffe94ffa0000</guid></item><item><title>“许多犹太人表示，如果极右或极左赢得选举，他们将离开法国”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-06-19/ty-article-podcast/many-jews-say-theyll-leave-france-if-the-far-right-or-extreme-left-win-the-election/00000190-2fe3-dc02-a7d8-eff7030c0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 15:21:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-06-19/ty-article-podcast/many-jews-say-theyll-leave-france-if-the-far-right-or-extreme-left-win-the-election/00000190-2fe3-dc02-a7d8-eff7030c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列表示计划建立一个替代红十字会的机构来探视巴勒斯坦囚犯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-planning-to-establish-alternative-to-red-cross-for-visits-to-palestinian-prisoners/00000190-30d3-d700-a7f0-bdf388410000</link><description>自加沙战争爆发以来，红十字会已停止探视被关押在以色列的巴勒斯坦人。以色列没有提供替代机制的细节，但国土报了解到，一个选择是法官和外国外交官的访问。以色列民权组织称此举违反国际法</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 15:08:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-planning-to-establish-alternative-to-red-cross-for-visits-to-palestinian-prisoners/00000190-30d3-d700-a7f0-bdf388410000</guid></item><item><title>以色列阿拉伯犹太运动员逆流而行：“我是融合的伟大证明”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-arab-jewish-athlete-swims-against-the-current-im-great-proof-of-integration/00000190-308c-d5f5-a5d6-f9ee0e120000</link><description>亚当·马拉纳 (Adam Maraana) 的父亲是穆斯林，母亲是犹太教徒，他将成为半个世纪以来第一位代表以色列参加奥运会的阿拉伯运动员。他说，在这个黑暗时期，他也能成为一名成功的“迷你大使”</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 14:54:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-arab-jewish-athlete-swims-against-the-current-im-great-proof-of-integration/00000190-308c-d5f5-a5d6-f9ee0e120000</guid></item><item><title>“不可能”：布鲁塞尔以加沙战争期间安全原因为由拒绝主办比利时与以色列的比赛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-06-19/ty-article/impossible-brussels-declines-to-host-belgium-israel-match-citing-security-reasons/00000190-30c3-d5f5-a5d6-f9ebbe9b0000</link><description>该市最高体育官员表示，“很明显，宣布在首都举行这样一场比赛无疑会引发大规模示威活动。”布鲁塞尔甚至在加沙战争爆发之前就已处于安全戒备状态，比利时多次遭受极端主义袭击</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 14:27:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-06-19/ty-article/impossible-brussels-declines-to-host-belgium-israel-match-citing-security-reasons/00000190-30c3-d5f5-a5d6-f9ebbe9b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列是否已成为加沙旁边的“利益区”，否认巴勒斯坦人的苦难？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/has-israel-become-a-zone-of-interest-next-to-gaza-in-denial-of-palestinian-suffering/00000190-3008-d700-a7f0-bdea2b3f0000</link><description>一张将以色列郁郁葱葱的向日葵田与加沙废墟并列的照片在网上疯传，人们将其与一部讲述奥斯威辛附近纳粹指挥官田园风光的奥斯卡获奖影片相比较。这场辩论提醒我们，图像不仅暗示什么，还隐藏什么</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 14:22:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/has-israel-become-a-zone-of-interest-next-to-gaza-in-denial-of-palestinian-suffering/00000190-3008-d700-a7f0-bdea2b3f0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡攻击拜登政府后，美国取消了与以色列就伊朗问题进行的战略会谈</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/u-s-nixes-strategic-talks-with-israel-on-iran-after-netanyahu-attacks-biden/00000190-30a8-d340-a1f8-38ac9f9f0000</link><description>一名以色列高级官员表示，内塔尼亚胡指责美国扣留以色列武器，这损害了数周来的协调努力；以色列总理此后收回了他的主张</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 14:01:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/u-s-nixes-strategic-talks-with-israel-on-iran-after-netanyahu-attacks-biden/00000190-30a8-d340-a1f8-38ac9f9f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列考古学家一劳永逸地证明：人类对巨型动物的灭绝负有责任</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-06-19/ty-article-magazine/israeli-scientists-show-definitively-humans-were-responsible-for-megafauna-extinction/00000190-2fbb-d700-a7f0-affbb2ef0000</link><description>特拉维夫大学的米基·本多尔和兰·巴尔凯并没有打算解决灭绝难题。但是在研究人类进化时，我们的衣柜里突然出现了一个巨大的骨架</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 13:27:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-06-19/ty-article-magazine/israeli-scientists-show-definitively-humans-were-responsible-for-megafauna-extinction/00000190-2fbb-d700-a7f0-affbb2ef0000</guid></item><item><title>不完全是圣殿：为什么以色列的犹太教堂如此没有吸引力？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/not-exactly-temples-why-are-israels-synagogues-so-unattractive/00000190-2b27-d340-a1f8-2b2725ec0000</link><description>虽然世界各地的犹太教堂都富丽堂皇，但以色列的情况却大不相同。做错了什么？</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 13:10:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/not-exactly-temples-why-are-israels-synagogues-so-unattractive/00000190-2b27-d340-a1f8-2b2725ec0000</guid></item><item><title>卫星图像显示黎巴嫩南部村庄遭到破坏</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-06-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/satellite-images-show-devastation-in-the-villages-of-southern-lebanon/00000190-302d-d39e-a999-76ef9a070000</link><description>以色列对真主党大火的反应已导致 10 万黎巴嫩人撤离。南部数千栋房屋被完全摧毁，损失达数十亿美元</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 12:12:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-06-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/satellite-images-show-devastation-in-the-villages-of-southern-lebanon/00000190-302d-d39e-a999-76ef9a070000</guid></item><item><title>“拉比法”危机表明内塔尼亚胡是多么容易受到极端正统派的勒索</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/crisis-over-rabbis-law-shows-how-vulnerable-netanyahu-is-to-extortion-by-ultra-orthodox/00000190-2f45-d340-a1f8-2f457d190000</link><description>在充满死亡和悲伤的时刻，内塔尼亚胡的联盟正在自杀，因为一项立法的目标是为极端正统政党创造大量就业机会。然而，几名“反叛”利库德集团议员代表了政党选民的强烈情绪，他们再也无法忍受恶心了</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 08:51:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/crisis-over-rabbis-law-shows-how-vulnerable-netanyahu-is-to-extortion-by-ultra-orthodox/00000190-2f45-d340-a1f8-2f457d190000</guid></item><item><title>ADL 因以色列可靠性问题和反犹太主义而面临维基百科禁令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/adl-faces-wikipedia-ban-over-reliability-concerns-on-israel-antisemitism/00000190-2f1d-d2ff-a5d1-7fdf29a30000</link><description>一位编辑写道，“反诽谤联盟似乎不再遵守反犹太主义的严肃、主流和学术上令人信服的定义”，他要求讨论反犹太主义的请求最终导致了禁令的实施。</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 07:08:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/adl-faces-wikipedia-ban-over-reliability-concerns-on-israel-antisemitism/00000190-2f1d-d2ff-a5d1-7fdf29a30000</guid></item></channel></rss>